Hi Folks,

Anyone here have idea how we can display the Company's Deals that was associated in the contact logged in the page (membership page)

{% set associated_deals = crm_associations(request.contact.contact_vid, 'HubSpot_DEFINED', 4, 'dealname,amount,dealstage,createdate,closedate') %}

And here's it all together:
```{% set associated_companies = crm_associations(contact.hs_object_id, "HubSpot_DEFINED", 1, "limit=3", "name", false) %}

{{ associated_companies }}

{% set associated_deals = crm_associations(associated_companies.results[0].id, 'HubSpot_DEFINED', 6, "", 'dealname,amount,dealstage,createdate,closedate') %}

{{associated_deals}}```

```{% set associated_companies = crm_associations(contact.hs_object_id, "HubSpot_DEFINED", 1, "limit=3", "name", false) %}

{{ associated_companies }}

{% set company_deals = crm_associations(associated_companies.results[0].id, 'HubSpot_DEFINED', 6, "", 'dealname,amount,dealstage,createdate,closedate') %}
&lt;h3&gt;Company Deals&lt;/h3&gt;
{{company_deals}}

&lt;h3&gt;Contact Deals&lt;/h3&gt;
{% set contact_deals = crm_associations(contact.hs_object_id, 'HubSpot_DEFINED', 4, "", 'dealname,amount,dealstage,createdate,closedate') %}
{{contact_deals}}```

This doesn't account for duplicats but it will work:
```{% set associated_companies = crm_associations(contact.hs_object_id, "HubSpot_DEFINED", 1, "limit=3", "name", false) %}

{{ associated_companies }}

{% set company_deals = crm_associations(associated_companies.results[0].id, 'HubSpot_DEFINED', 6, "", 'dealname,amount,dealstage,createdate,closedate') %}
&lt;h3&gt;Company Deals&lt;/h3&gt;
{{company_deals}}

&lt;h3&gt;Contact Deals&lt;/h3&gt;
{% set contact_deals = crm_associations(contact.hs_object_id, 'HubSpot_DEFINED', 4, "", 'dealname,amount,dealstage,createdate,closedate') %}
{{contact_deals}}

{% set deals = [] %}

{% do deals.extend(company_deals.results) %}

{% do deals.extend(contact_deals.results) %}

ALL DEALS
{{ deals }}```

Try this:
```{% set associated_companies = crm_associations(contact.hs_object_id, "HubSpot_DEFINED", 1, "limit=3", "name", false) %}

{% set company_deals = crm_associations(associated_companies.results[0].id, 'HubSpot_DEFINED', 6, "", 'dealname,amount,dealstage,createdate,closedate') %}
&lt;h3&gt;Company Deals&lt;/h3&gt;
{{company_deals}}

&lt;h3&gt;Contact Deals&lt;/h3&gt;
{% set contact_deals = crm_associations(contact.hs_object_id, 'HubSpot_DEFINED', 4, "", 'dealname,amount,dealstage,createdate,closedate') %}
{{contact_deals}}

{% set deals = [] %}

{% do deals.extend(company_deals.results) %}

{% do deals.extend(contact_deals.results) %}

&lt;h3&gt;All Deals&lt;/h3&gt;
{{ deals }}```
